description: TypeScript standards across JobOS monorepo
globs: "**/*.{ts,tsx}"
alwaysApply: false
---

# TypeScript

- Strict mode enabled in all tsconfig files.
- Shared domain types in packages/types — import, don't redefine.
- Prefer interfaces for object shapes; enums for fixed sets (PipelineStage, etc.).
- Use Zod for runtime validation at API boundaries.
- No implicit any — explicit types on public APIs.
- Use path aliases consistently per app (@/* in Next.js apps).
